  "title": "2000s Edition",
  "description": "Legacy Console Edition if it was made for 2000s-era PC's and the 6th Generation of Video Game Consoles! (An Official Legacy4J Project)",
  "body": "<p align=\"center\">\n  <span style=\"display: inline-block; margin: 0 10px;\">\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/modpack/rekindled-legacy\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/0692100a197e1d07829702d4620bea7695293521.png\" width=\"1000\"/>\n      </span></a><br/>\n</p>\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <span style=\"display: inline-block; margin: 0 10px;\">\n    <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/projects/2000s-edition\">\n      <img height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy-minimal/available/modrinth_vector.svg\"/>\n    </a>\n      </span>\n  <span style=\"display: inline-block; margin: 0 10px;\">\n    <a href=\"https://fabricmc.net\">\n      <img height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy-minimal/supported/fabric_vector.svg\"/>\n    </a>\n  </span>\n  <span style=\"display: inline-block; margin: 0 10px;\">\n    <a href=\"https://discord.gg/h6DBxNbPzY\">\n      <img height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy-minimal/social/discord-singular_vector.svg\"/>\n    </a>\n  </span>\n  <span style=\"display: inline-block; margin: 0 10px;\">\n    <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/modpack/adrenaline\">\n      <img height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy-minimal/built-with/adrenaline_vector.svg\"/>\n    </a>\n  </span>\n  <span style=\"display: inline-block; margin: 0 10px;\">\n    <a href=\"https://git.nostalgica.net/Lasting-Legacy/Lasting-Legacy-Monorepo/src/branch/main/modpacks/2k\">\n      <img height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy-minimal/available/git_vector.svg\"/>\n    </a>\n      </span>\n  <span style=\"display: inline-block; margin: 0 10px;\">\n    <a href=\"https://docs.nostalgica.net/modpacks/2000s-edition/overview\">\n      <img height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy-minimal/documentation/readthedocs_vector.svg\">\n     </a>\n</p>\n  <p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/abe663645bbb2a2b7c598c6af3c39cc8646cccc3.png\" width=\"500\"/>\n  </p>\n    \nThis modpacks aims into recreate TU9 but with a twist, what if it released in the 2000s? This modpacks changes the User Interface, Creative Listing, Crafting Listing, Sounds, and everything else that makes it like TU9 from Legacy Console Edition.\n\nCheck out the SteamGridDB assets for 2000s Edition [here](https://www.steamgriddb.com/collection/24200)! <br>\n<br/>\n<p align=\"center\">\n<img src= \"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/a883a51d2233102e9c0bd21770a431c55d2da29c.png\" width=\"500\"/>\n</p>\n    \n\nThe Installation guide is on the [Lasting Legacy Docs](https://docs.nostalgica.net/modpacks/installation), but the recommended ways to install 2000s Edition is through Prism Launcher, ATLauncher, and Modrinth.\n\n<br/>\n<p align=\"center\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/f71b9bbdfac6d7b666385adaa94930c0df9ff1da.png\" width=\"500\"/> <br>\n</p>\n\n### TU9 Accuracy\nIt aims to recreate Title Update 9 with it's User Interface, items, blocks, terrain, and mob spawning. There's some that can't really be recreated such as the Inventory Screen, and some are altered such as the Title Screen.\n\n### Open Source\n2000s Edition is mostly used of open-source mods and resource packs. It's avaiable on Nostalgica Forgejo, which gives you the ability to see the code and contribute to the modpack. It's also avaiable as a packwiz project.\n\n<br/>\n<p align=\"center\">\n<img src= \"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/5fd71075d2321d8cef562b6d22f182911e1f7005.png\" width=\"500\"/>\n</p>\n\n- angrybirds0706 for some of the configs and jsons <br>\n- ren for making the Title Screen <br>\n- Cjnator38 for making the blocky edition titles <br>\n- Wilyicaro for making Legacy4J and making this modpack possible <br>\n- AzaleaCatgirl99 for letting the use of the assets from Reborn Resources <br>\n<br>\n<p align=\"center\">\n<img src= \"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/5a97cb13625747dfce03aefeda3ff5666def15ff.png\" width=\"500\"/> <br/>\n</p>\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <span style=\"display: inline-block; margin: 0 10px;\">\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/collection/72AM2FL7\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/4c598b3feda45a05b79876158d11d47581a6652c.png\" width=\"750\"/>\n      </span></a><br/>\n    </p>",
